                                                                                                       public-key certificate by the public-key owner, the owner’s representative, the CA, or a
                                                                                                       certificate repository (i.e., a directory): the mandatory assurances listed in Section 8.1.5.1.1
                                                                                                       that are not provided by the CA (e.g., public-key validation) shall be provided to or
